{"tid":252892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊網鼓勵同事捐血 捐血1次 放假1天","createTime":"2017-05-22T02:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T03:34:52.000Z","uid":74293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f81ddfb17b0d877c5aed7d2475cb172d501a96cd","tid":252892,"uid":74293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"旅遊網鼓勵同事捐血 捐血1次 放假1天<br />\n<br />\n2017/05/22<br />\n<br />\n最近唔少人都關注血庫存量不足嘅問題，旅遊體驗平台KKday由今個月開始推出捐血優惠，只要在捐血時影張相，上載到個人社交網站，標籤「KKday」同埋hashtag「#KKdayblooddono」，就可以獲得KKday全綫行程九五折優惠。<br />\n<br />\n黛安見到個優惠咁有意義，特登打咗去同KKday嘅公關好友傾咗陣，原來KKday為咗鼓勵同事捐血，今個月開始內部都實行「捐血獎勵計劃」，除咗原本嘅Annual Leave，每次捐血都可以額外獲得1日有薪「捐血假」，捐血當日仲可以多半日假期，等同事可以休息下，員工只需要在捐血前通知人事部就OK。好友仲話，KKday CEO陳明明今日仲會身體力行，「拉大隊」同員工一齊捐血𠻹！<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 黛安 消息特靈八卦公關 <br />\n欄名: 八卦名利場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1818092/%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%B6%B2%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%8D%90%E8%A1%80%20%E6%8D%90%E8%A1%801%E6%AC%A1%20%E6%94%BE%E5%81%871%E5%A4%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1818092%2F%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%258D%2590%25E8%25A1%2580%2520%25E6%258D%2590%25E8%25A1%25801%25E6%25AC%25A1%2520%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2581%25871%25E5%25A4%25A9&d=q6lxkNJLkMCZuErjOs479Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e466ec80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1818092/%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%B6%B2%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%8D%90%E8%A1%80%20%E6%8D%90%E8%A1%801%E6%AC%A1%20%E6%94%BE%E5%81%871%E5%A4%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上埋新聞 優惠唔知係真定假 有無捐開血嘅巴去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce9dbad1245f44869261035cba13f159c780cdf","tid":252892,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"Kkday定klook好用d?"